-- Vestas Shares Fall 12% in Copenhagen After Loss Widens, CFO Quits
-- B y   A l e x   M o r a l e s
-- 2012-02-08T08:05:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-08/vestas-shares-fall-12-after-loss-widens-cfo-quits.html
Vestas Wind Systems A/S (VWS)  shares fell
as much as 12 percent in Copenhagen after the company announced
a loss four times wider than analyst forecasts for 2011 and
Chief Financial Officer Henrik Norremark stepped down.  To contact the reporter on this story:
